  "AsteroidExpeditionObj2title": "Objective 2: Reach the Anomaly",
  "AsteroidExpeditionObj2desc": "Excavate into the asteroid and reach the anomaly.",
  "AsteroidExpeditionObj3title": "Objective 3: Fix the Science Ship",
  "AsteroidExpeditionObj3desc": "We need to investigate this more closely. Unfortunately one of our scientist crashed our science ship, please locate it, fix it and then bring it to the anomaly.",
