  "AsteroidExpeditionObj3Bdesc": "• Fix Cockpit",
  "AsteroidExpeditionObj4title": "Objective 4: Return to the Anomaly",
  "AsteroidExpeditionObj4desc": "Move the Science Ship back to the anomaly. Keep the cockpit intact!",
  "DetonationDetectedObj1Title": "Objective 1: Detonation Detected",
  "DetonationDetectedObj1Desc": "A large explosion was detected at a nearby outpost, head to the indicated location on your HUD.",
  "DetonationDetectedObj2Title": "Objective 2: Investigate Damaged Hab",
  "DetonationDetectedObj2Desc": "Locate and investigate the damaged hab module. Do not destroy the toilet or shower they are valuable scrap!",
  "DetonationDetectedObj3Title": "Objective 3: Finish the Projections",
  "DetonationDetectedObj3Desc": "While constructing their outpost a large explosion happened in one of their habs. Help them out and weld up the projected blocks on the nearby habs. The required raw materials should be nearby.",
  "DetonationDetectedObj3aDesc": "• Finish Hab 1",
  "DetonationDetectedObj3bDesc": "• Finish Hab 2",
  "DetonationDetectedObj4Title": "Objective 4:  Move the Damaged Hab",
  "DetonationDetectedObj4Desc": "Disconnect the damaged hab from its foundations and move it away from the asteroid for the salvage teams to collect.",
  "StrandedFreighterObj1Title": "Objective 1: Locate the Cargo Outpost",
  "StrandedFreighterObj1Desc": "Fly to the marker Indicated on your HUD",
  "StrandedFreighterObj2Title": "Objective 2: Download the Accident Report",
  "StrandedFreighterObj2Desc": "Enter the control seat in the outpost to download the freighter's accident report",
  "StrandedFreighterObj3Title": "Objective 3: Accident Report",
  "StrandedFreighterObj3Desc": "Accident Report: Ship stopped responding to controls | Ran aground | Gyroscopes damaged | x6 Cargo lost",
  "StrandedFreighterObj3aDesc": "• Locate Iron, Nickel and Copper from the nearby asteroid and repair the marked gyroscopes",
  "StrandedFreighterObj3bDesc": "• Pilot the freighter to the docking clamp indicated on your HUD",
  "StrandedFreighterObj3cDesc": "• Enter the Tug's cockpit and fly over the asteroid",
  "StrandedFreighterObj3dDesc": "• Retrieve the freighter's cargo and place them in the associated colored storage areas.",
  "SectorFoundationsObj1title": "Objective 1: Locate the Supply Base",
  "SectorFoundationsObj1desc": "The sectors colonization requires a supply base, manufacturing site and a mining site. We started working on these but had to divert our manpower to help with a ship accident. We need you to set up antennas and power systems to these sites so they don't become another failed attempt to colonize the sector.",
  "SectorFoundationsObj1Atitle": "Objective 1A: Supply Base",
  "SectorFoundationsObj1Adesc": "Construct the marked battery and antenna for the supply base. There should be a Bullfrog cargo shuttle with all required components in it.",
  "SectorFoundationsObj1Btitle": "Objective 1B: Manufacturing Site",
  "SectorFoundationsObj1Bdesc": "The reactor on the manufacturing site was left unfinished. Use the supplies in the shuttle to construct it and look for uranium around the manufacturing site to power the reactor.",
  "SectorFoundationsObj1Ctitle": "Objective 1C: Mining Site",
  "SectorFoundationsObj1Cdesc": "Construct the marked battery and antenna for the mining site.",
  "SectorFoundationsObj2title": "Objective 2: Unknown Signal",
  "SectorFoundationsObj2desc": "The antenna is picking up a faint signal inside nearby asteroid. Please investigate the signal source.",
  "SectorFoundationsObj3title": "Objective 3: Deliver the unknown ship back to supply base",
  "SectorFoundationsObj3desc": "Seems like whoever set up the base, was excavating the asteroid and left in a hurry. Please retrieve the small shuttle back to the supply base for study. Salvage parts from the Bullfrog cargo shuttle, if necessary.",
  "ShipBreakersObj1title": "Objective 1: Locate the Construction Yard",
  "ShipBreakersObj1desc": "A Hydrogen Hauler was damaged to a point it's no use repairing it. The ship is currently blocking a construction yard so if you help dismantling the ship, you can keep the components.",
  "ShipBreakersObj2title": "Objective 2: Salvage marked parts",
  "ShipBreakersObj2desc": "Grind down the marked blocks. You can keep the components or if you don't need them, store them to the cargo container in the hangar.",
  "ShipBreakersObj2Adesc": "• Salvage Gravity Generator",
  "ShipBreakersObj2Bdesc": "• Salvage Main Thruster",
  "ShipBreakersObj2Cdesc": "• Salvage Side Thruster",
  "ShipBreakersObj2Ddesc": "• Salvage Reactor",
  "ShipBreakersObj2Edesc": "• Salvage Battery",
  "ShipBreakersObj3title": "Objective 3: Point of Interest",
  "ShipBreakersObj3desc": "We managed to retrieve coordinates from the small shuttle that you retrieved to the supply base in the previous contract. The coordinates are near your current location, so might be worth checking out. ",
  "IncidentTitle": "Engineering - Red Ship: The Incident",
  "IncidentDesc": "A clash between two factions has left tensions high. One side denies involvement, claiming renegades used a recently captured ship to destabilize the sector. Repair the vessel and deliver it to the nearby shipyard for analysis.",
  "IncidentObj1title": "Objective 1: Investigate the Incident Site",
  "IncidentObj1desc": "A clash between two factions has left tensions high. One side denies involvement, claiming renegades used a recently captured ship to destabilize the sector. Repair the vessel and deliver it to the nearby shipyard for analysis.",
  "IncidentObj2title": "Objective 2: Move the red ship to nearby shipyard",
  "IncidentObj2desc": "Restore the ship’s mobility by constructing projected thrusters and repairing the control seat, gyroscope, and reactor. Salvage components from nearby debris to complete the repairs.",
  "IncidentObj3title": "Objective 3: Upload the Ship’s Navigation Data",
  "IncidentObj3desc": "Complete the unfinished assembler by gathering resources, then use it to manufacture the components needed to build the antenna.",
  "TestLaunchTitle": "Engineering - Test Launch",
  "TestLaunchDesc": "The site was evacuated after the recent incident. Restore power, complete the probe, and launch it to secure the test data.",
  "TestLaunchObj1title": "Objective 1: Locate the Probe Testing Site",
  "TestLaunchObj1desc": "The site was evacuated after the recent incident. Restore power, complete the probe, and launch it to secure the test data.",
  "TestLaunchObj2title": "Objective 2: Restore Power to the Launch Site",
  "TestLaunchObj2desc": "The reactor is unfinished, preventing use of the assembler and refinery. Search the old mining tunnels for a decommissioned reactor, salvage the needed components, and use them to complete the base reactor.",
  "TestLaunchObj3title": "Objective 3: Construct the Probe",
  "TestLaunchObj3desc": "Complete the ore detector and battery for the probe. The assembler and refinery next to the probe have the required components queued. Locate the missing ores in the mining tunnels.",
  "TestLaunchObj4title": "Objective 4: Launch the Probe",
  "TestLaunchObj4desc": "Enter the control seat and press {Control:ToggleParkingBrakes} to unlock the connector to launch the probe."
 
}